{"id":220,"parent_id":218,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":220,"title":"Judges 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Judg.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","An angel rebukes Israel for not serving the Lord—As a pattern of future events, a new generation arises that forsakes the Lord and serves Baal and Ashtaroth—The Lord is angry with the children of Israel and ceases to preserve them—He raises up judges to guide and lead them—The Canaanites are left in the land to test Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.1","order":"02.08.002.19188"},["b","1"],"And an angel of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came up from Gilgal to Bochim, and said, I made you to go up out of Egypt, and have brought you unto the land which I sware unto your fathers; and I said, I will never",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"break"],"my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"covenant"],"with you."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.2","order":"02.08.002.19189"},["b","2"],"And ye shall make no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"league"],"with the inhabitants of this land; ye shall throw down their altars: but ye have not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"obeyed"],"my voice: why have ye done this?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.3","order":"02.08.002.19190"},["b","3"],"Wherefore I also said, I will not drive them out from before you; but they shall be",["i","as thorns"],"in your sides, and their gods shall be a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"snare"],"unto you."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.4","order":"02.08.002.19191"},["b","4"],"And it came to pass, when the angel of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake these words unto all the children of Israel, that the people lifted up their voice, and wept."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.5","order":"02.08.002.19192"},["b","5"],"And they called the name of that place Bochim: and they sacrificed there unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.6","order":"02.08.002.19193"},["b","6"],"¶And when Joshua had let the people go, the children of Israel went every man unto his inheritance to possess the land."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.7","order":"02.08.002.19194"},["b","7"],"And the people",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"served"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"all the days of Joshua, and all the days of the elders that outlived Joshua, who had seen all the great works of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that he did for Israel."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.8","order":"02.08.002.19195"},["b","8"],"And Joshua the son of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Nun"],", the servant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", died,",["i","being"],"an hundred and ten years old."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.9","order":"02.08.002.19196"},["b","9"],"And they buried him in the border of his inheritance in Timnath-heres, in the mount of Ephraim, on the north side of the hill Gaash."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.10","order":"02.08.002.19197"},["b","10"],"And also all that generation were gathered unto their fathers: and there arose another generation after them, which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"knew not"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", nor yet the works which he had done for Israel."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.11","order":"02.08.002.19198"},["b","11"],"¶And the children of Israel did evil in the sight of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and served Baalim:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.12","order":"02.08.002.19199"},["b","12"],"And they forsook the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of their fathers, which brought them out of the land of Egypt, and followed other gods, of the gods of the people that",["i","were"],"round about them, and bowed themselves unto them, and provoked the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"anger"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.13","order":"02.08.002.19200"},["b","13"],"And they forsook the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and served",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Baal"],"and Ashtaroth."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.14","order":"02.08.002.19201"},["b","14"],"¶And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"anger"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was hot against Israel, and he delivered them into the hands of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"spoilers"],"that spoiled them, and he sold them into the hands of their enemies round about, so that they could not any longer stand before their enemies."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.15","order":"02.08.002.19202"},["b","15"],"Whithersoever they went out, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"hand"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was against them for evil, as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had said, and as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had sworn unto them: and they were greatly distressed."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.16","order":"02.08.002.19203"},["b","16"],"¶Nevertheless the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"raised up",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"judges"],", which",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"delivered"],"them out of the hand of those that spoiled them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.17","order":"02.08.002.19204"},["b","17"],"And yet they would not hearken unto their judges, but they went a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"whoring"],"after other",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"gods"],", and bowed themselves unto them: they turned",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"quickly"],"out of the way which their fathers walked in, obeying the commandments of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],";",["i","but"],"they did not so."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.18","order":"02.08.002.19205"},["b","18"],"And when the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"raised them up judges, then the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was with the judge, and delivered them out of the hand of their enemies all the days of the judge:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"for it repented"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"because of their groanings by reason of them that oppressed them and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"vexed"],"them."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.19","order":"02.08.002.19206"},["b","19"],"And it came to pass, when the judge was dead,",["i","that"],"they returned, and corrupted",["i","themselves"],"more than their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"fathers"],", in following other gods to serve them, and to bow down unto them; they ceased not from their own doings, nor from their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"stubborn"],"way."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.20","order":"02.08.002.19207"},["b","20"],"¶And the anger of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was hot against Israel; and he said, Because that this people hath transgressed my covenant which I commanded their fathers, and have not hearkened unto my voice;"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.21","order":"02.08.002.19208"},["b","21"],"I also will not henceforth drive out any from before them of the nations which Joshua left when he died:"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.22","order":"02.08.002.19209"},["b","22"],"That through them I may",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"prove"],"Israel, whether they will keep the way of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"walk"],"therein, as their fathers did keep",["i","it,"],"or not."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.23","order":"02.08.002.19210"},["b","23"],"Therefore the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"left those nations, without driving them out hastily; neither delivered he them into the hand of Joshua."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.1a","order":"02.08.002.19211"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/31.16"},"Deut. 31:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.1b","order":"02.08.002.19213"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abrahamic-covenant"},"TG Abrahamic Covenant"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covenants"},"Covenants"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.2a","order":"02.08.002.19215"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.12"},"Ex. 34:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/9.7"},"Josh. 9:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.2b","order":"02.08.002.19217"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.3a","order":"02.08.002.19219"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/23.33"},"Ex. 23:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.7a","order":"02.08.002.19221"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/24.31"},"Josh. 24:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.8a","order":"02.08.002.19223"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/13.16"},"Num. 13:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/34.9"},"Deut. 34:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.10a","order":"02.08.002.19225"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-knowledge-about"},"TG God, Knowledge about"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.12a","order":"02.08.002.19227"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/anger"},"TG Anger"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.13a","order":"02.08.002.19229"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/7.4"},"1 Sam. 7:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.14a","order":"02.08.002.19231"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.2.1-3"},"D&C 95:2 (1–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.21"},"98:21"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-indignation-of"},"TG God, Indignation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.14b","order":"02.08.002.19233"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/9.27"},"Neh. 9:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.15a","order":"02.08.002.19235"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.3.3-46"},"Lev. 26:3 (3–46)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.16a","order":"02.08.002.19237"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ruth/1.1"},"Ruth 1:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.11"},"2 Sam. 7:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/29.41.41,44"},"Mosiah 29:41 (41, 44)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.16b","order":"02.08.002.19239"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.17a","order":"02.08.002.19241"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.37"},"2 Ne. 9:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/7.6"},"Alma 7:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/6.31"},"Hel. 6:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.17b","order":"02.08.002.19243"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.15"},"Ex. 34:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.17c","order":"02.08.002.19245"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.8"},"Alma 46:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.4.2-5"},"Hel. 12:4 (2–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.18a","order":"02.08.002.19247"},["b","18a"],"The Hebrew root means “to be sorry,” “moved to pity,” or “have compassion.”",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.45"},"Ps. 106:45"],".",["span.small","JST"],"Judg. 2:18 … for the Lord",["i","hearkened"],"because of …"],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.18b","order":"02.08.002.19249"},["b","18b"],["span.small","HEB"],"crushed."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.19a","order":"02.08.002.19251"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/23.32.30-32"},"Matt. 23:32 (30–32)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.19b","order":"02.08.002.19253"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stubbornness"},"TG Stubbornness"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.22a","order":"02.08.002.19255"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.24.23-24"},"1 Ne. 2:24 (23–24)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.22b","order":"02.08.002.19257"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."]]}
